description: Product Description This new Elbow Grease Mould & Mildew Stain Remover is another miracle product from Elbow Grease. Scientifically designed to remove mould stains on a range of surfaces. Keep tiles, sinks, baths and toilets sparkling clean, free from mould and mildew stains. Perfect for both indoor and outdoor use, the Elbow Grease Mould & Mildew Stain Remover contains bleach, it is ideally suited for use on baths, toilets, showers and tiles. The Elbow Grease Mould & Mildew Stain Remover will get your garden furniture and outdoor play equipment clean and fresh for the summer season.
